00:34:29,810 --> 00:34:31,771
So we actually ended up taking off some

868
00:34:31,811 --> 00:34:32,752
spaces from the sides.

869
00:34:34,514 --> 00:34:39,578
But this ended up being okay because we found that if we took space off the sides, it still

870
00:34:39,638 --> 00:34:40,098
felt right.

871
00:34:40,478 --> 00:34:44,501
It still felt like Manhattan and it didn't really disrupt the layout or it didn't disrupt

872
00:34:44,581 --> 00:34:46,082
our landmarks very much.

873
00:34:46,942 --> 00:34:51,325
