00:41:35,247 --> 00:41:40,110
And so we had idealized metrics that we wanted to hit.

1028
00:41:40,450 --> 00:41:42,011
And we knew there was ability to scale there.

1029
00:41:42,243 --> 00:41:45,405
And then ultimately, one of the things we do at Insomniac

1030
00:41:45,445 --> 00:41:47,027
is just sort of rely on our awesome engine

1031
00:41:47,047 --> 00:41:47,787
and technical teams.

1032
00:41:48,968 --> 00:41:49,889
I don't know what those guys do.

1033
00:41:49,969 --> 00:41:50,649
I think they're wizards.

1034
00:41:51,890 --> 00:41:53,351
But I just say, hey, I want to do this thing.

