00:41:54,552 --> 00:41:55,053
Can you do it?

1037
00:41:55,113 --> 00:41:56,074
And somehow they figure it out.

1038
00:41:56,174 --> 00:41:59,416
Hi.

1039
00:41:59,997 --> 00:42:01,177
What part of the process do you start

