1087
00:43:59,528 --> 00:44:03,111
Because what you'll find is by researching for one game,

1088
00:44:03,131 --> 00:44:06,554
you may see an interesting or unique element

1089
00:44:06,874 --> 00:44:08,035
that you can maybe remember.

1090
00:44:08,135 --> 00:44:09,777
And then you can come back and revisit

1091
00:44:09,817 --> 00:44:11,478
that when you are doing research for another thing.

1092
00:44:11,558 --> 00:44:13,980
So it just helps us try to, as much as you can,

1093
00:44:14,061 --> 00:44:15,882
try to build that repertoire of interesting mechanics

1094
00:44:15,922 --> 00:44:17,364
and interesting games to reference.

1095
00:44:18,424 --> 00:44:18,645
Thank you.

1096
00:44:21,850 --> 00:44:25,553
Hi, I love all the transference from Sunset Overdrive to Spider-Man.

1097
00:44:25,573 --> 00:44:27,075
That seems to be like a key thing.

1098
00:44:27,795 --> 00:44:30,397
