00:44:46,975 --> 00:44:49,235
with just sort of the basic principles of the design

1105
00:44:49,435 --> 00:44:54,436
and trying to build the diverse and different layouts

1106
00:44:54,476 --> 00:44:55,337
for the world.

1107
00:44:56,017 --> 00:44:57,417
There are a lot of other principles

