1111
00:45:05,679 --> 00:45:08,799
I was really big on just adding trees and waterfalls

1112
00:45:08,879 --> 00:45:11,080
and anything that could anywhere we wanted.

1113
00:45:11,848 --> 00:45:16,272
And for Manhattan, I was super big on Central Park.

1114
00:45:16,592 --> 00:45:20,876
I wanted Central Park to be this really beautiful, natural space.

1115
00:45:21,157 --> 00:45:23,579
Because I felt like it was important that we gave players

1116
00:45:23,639 --> 00:45:24,920
a break from the city.

1117
00:45:25,841 --> 00:45:29,044
And so a lot of the effort that went behind making sure

1118
00:45:29,064 --> 00:45:31,326
that Central Park is actually, compared

1119
00:45:31,346 --> 00:45:33,668
to the rest of the map, a pretty massive space, even though it's

1120
00:45:33,688 --> 00:45:34,990
totally different from everything else.

1121
00:45:35,390 --> 00:45:36,251
A lot of that comes from.

1122
00:45:37,014 --> 00:45:39,777
all the desires to create natural spaces in Sunset Overdrive.

1123
00:45:39,817 --> 00:45:41,699
And so I think that was a big inspiration that was brought over.

